{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"strong"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray<MLNOfflinePack *>"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"packs"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property is set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", indicating that the receiver does not yet know"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the existing packs, for an undefined amount of time starting from the moment"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the shared offline storage object is initialized until the packs are fetched"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"from the database. After that point, this property is always non-nil, but it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"may be empty to indicate that no packs are present."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To detect when the shared offline storage object has finished loading its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property, observe KVO change notifications on the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" key path."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The initial load results in an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSKeyValueChangeSetting"},{"type":"text","text":" change."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/packs"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/packs"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflineStorage(py)packs","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"packs"}],"title":"packs","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"packs"}],"symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of all known offline packs, in the order in which they were created."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/packs":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of all known offline packs, in the order in which they were created."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/packs","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/packs","type":"topic","title":"packs","fragments":[{"text":"packs","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"role":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}]}}}